name: NOVEMBER- 300x103 size - Ad Space for www.sianvictoria.com Blog
description:
This sale is for the month of NOVEMBER to have your ad banner on my website under the “Your Space” section of my blog. Statistics coming soon!

My blog is still growing but I aim to do at least 5 blog posts a week.

Email sianvictoriablog@gmail.com with your banner and details you want me to tell my readers.
